{"tid":60001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"感動真人真事！","createTime":"2016-12-30T06:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T06:21:14.000Z","uid":37065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0004e7f9841243ca3de7a6ec1e9ee3b53e4af56e","tid":60001,"uid":37065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"真心，關愛係冇分國籍。<br />\n呢位先生連續讓座三次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次係太子站車廂好多人，一對老夫老妻拖住行李，出唔到個月台，行動不便。佢就幫手扶去月台。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （袋放係位上面，就去扶）<br />\n第二次係個阿婆，佢諗住坐，之後又主動起身讓座，幫手扶。<br />\n第三次係位女士，年紀唔係好大，但係都好有紳士風度。（發現有禮貌手，請佢坐）<br />\n其實我心諗有時候，連自己香港人都未必做到。<br />\n我睇住個經過，feel到好窩心。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/140802_cef62f88c4da78237f6deb5500bbda1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F140802_cef62f88c4da78237f6deb5500bbda1d.jpg&h=28cef4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d7ae04c10abd4fd3efa27bebdbcde3a51e54ca","tid":60001,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"好人無分國籍<br />\n歧視有分種族"}]}